data.description:
Gorgeous, well-maintained, open floor plan, 5-bedrooms, 3 full baths, 3 car garage-(50-amp connection) home situated on 1.5 acres in Deer Creek Farms! Step inside to find a dramatic ranch entry, vaulted ceilings in the living and dining room with large high-end Champion windows, refinished wood floors, great lighting and unobstructed views! 
3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms on the main.  The finished basement boosts 2 large bedrooms and 1 full bath.  And has ample space for an amazing entertaining, family room, recreation room, and etc. 
This home sits on an expansive corner lot with an abundance of independently irrigated trees, professionally landscaped as well as stunning mountain views. New roof 2023 with Class IV Shingles (Insurance savings) Relax on your large fully covered back deck or go to sit in the amazing fire pit. The 8 x12 shed has electricity - could be used for a she shed!  You have the option of adding extra storage buildings, there is plenty of room to for all of your toys or recreational vehicles (Full RV hookup). On those cooler evenings to keep your home cozy use one of two, top of the line pellet stoves. For your four-legged friends there is the dog run with a dog door access to garage. 
Easy access to Parker and Elizabeth, this really is country living at its finest.
VA Loan 3.1% APR assumption possible!  Fantastic location in a quiet neighborhood, minutes from schools (elementary, middle, and high school), grocery, and more.  No HOA!   VA Loan assumption possible!

All offer's due Sunday April 21st with an acceptance deadline Monday April 22nd 8 p.m.
